+ Class Properties

++ Public

* Solar_App::$layout_base -- The <base> href value for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_bottom -- An array of content for the layout <div id="bottom"> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_left -- An array of content for the layout <div id="left"> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_link -- An array of <link> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_meta -- An array of <meta> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_object -- An array of <object> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_right -- An array of content for the layout <div id="right"> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_script -- An array of <script> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_style -- An array of <style> tag values for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_title -- The <title> tag value for the layout <head> block.

* Solar_App::$layout_top -- An array of content for the layout <div id="top"> block.

++ Protected

* Solar_App::$_action -- The action being requested of (performed by) the application.

* Solar_App::$_action_default -- The default application action.

* Solar_App::$_action_info -- The info variables to use for actions.

* Solar_App::$_config -- User-provided configuration values.

* Solar_App::$_dir -- Base directory under which actions, views, etc. are located.

* Solar_App::$_info -- Application request parameters collected from the URI pathinfo.

* Solar_App::$_layout -- The name of the layout to use for the view, minus the .layout.php suffix.

* Solar_App::$_layout_dir -- Where the layout directory is located.

* Solar_App::$_layout_var -- The name of the variable where page content is placed in the layout.

* Solar_App::$_name -- The short-name of this application.

* Solar_App::$_query -- Application request parameters collected from the URI query string.

* Solar_App::$_view -- The name of the view to be rendered after the action, minus the .view.php suffix.

